{"tid":1589710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"300中學生樂富廣場合唱　","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T11:44:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"74e189f5e389d1ca111d263e8fa085a5e3a8cd6e","tid":1589710,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"有反對修例網民今日(23日)傍晚在黃大仙舉行名為「仙人學生交響曲」活動，約300名區內不同學校學生身穿校服在樂富廣場合唱不同歌曲，包括《願榮光歸香港》，而部分人戴着口罩、頭盔，高呼「光復香港，時代革命。五大訴求，缺一不可」等口號，不少路過市民及街坊駐足圍觀打氣。<br />\n<br />\n期間，他們在廣場頂層垂下一幅約4乘40米的黃色直幡，寫有「我願榮光歸香港」。期間數名學生用雷射筆照天花，有人大聲調侃「着火啦」，引起在場人士哄堂大笑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190923/photo/bkn-20190923182523355-0923_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190923190329\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190923%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190923182523355-0923_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190923190329&h=38a3edea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190923/photo/bkn-20190923182523355-0923_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190923190329\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190923%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190923182523355-0923_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190923190329&h=60bd44c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190923/mobile/bkn-20190923182523355-0923_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3fbe7c425ecf5ee4d7d70e2e473bb1e3ae0aa334","tid":1589710,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"0bf958ec070ff6ea822ab1a73f9d7d149e21665c","tid":1589710,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019